MICHAEL Things went badly in Palermo?
DON TOMMASSINO The younger men have no respect.
DON TOMMASSINO Things are changing; I don't know what will happen.
DON TOMMASSINO Michael, because of the wedding, people now know your name.
MICHAEL Is that why there are more men on the walls?
DON TOMMASSINO Even so, I don't think it is safe here anymore.
